NAME
    Attr/String -- implement string attribute using symlink 

METHODS
    set     -- set the attribute to the given string value
    clear   -- set the attribute to the empty value
    is      -- assert attribute has the given value
    show    -- print attribute value to stdout
    help    -- display this help screen

IMPLEMENTATION
    An Attr/String object is a symlink file with it's target set to a string
    value with prefix =.  The prefix is intended to make collisions with
    actual files unlikely. 

